===========================================================================
THIRD-PARTY COMPONENTS
===========================================================================

1. ORACLE OPTIMIZATION ENGINE (./oracle/)
   Originally from: Double Finance
   License: GNU General Public License v3.0
   Modifications: Integrated as tax optimization MCP server
   
   This component provides CBC solver-based portfolio optimization with
   advanced tax-aware rebalancing capabilities. It is a core dependency
   that requires this project to be licensed under GPL-3.0.

2. PYPORTFOLIOOPT
   Source: https://github.com/robertmartin8/PyPortfolioOpt
   License: MIT License
   Usage: Portfolio optimization algorithms (Efficient Frontier, Black-Litterman)

3. RISKFOLIO-LIB
   Source: https://github.com/dcajasn/Riskfolio-Lib
   License: BSD 3-Clause License
   Usage: Advanced risk measures and optimization methods

4. OPENBB PLATFORM
   Source: https://github.com/OpenBB-finance/OpenBB
   License: AGPL-3.0 (Community Edition)
   Usage: Market data access and financial analytics
   Note: Used via API/SDK, not distributed with this software

5. MODEL CONTEXT PROTOCOL (MCP)
   Source: https://modelcontextprotocol.io
   License: MIT License
   Copyright: Anthropic
   Usage: Server-client protocol for AI tool integration

